{
  "texts": [
    "Only RU and UA tweets of each user are considered.",
    "Effect sizes for both sample and behavioural changes extracted from the language model described in Section \"Language Modelling\" between key dates.",
    "All effect sizes are relative increases in the odds between the two respective dates.",
    "which 20 (1.7%) are significant (z > 1.96, p < 0.05).",
    "Hence, there are only very few UA tweeting users for which we can report a significant switch towards RU after the war."
  ]
}